<Page
    x:Class="moegirl_UWP.guanyu.weilai"
    xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
    xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml"
    xmlns:local="using:moegirl_UWP.guanyu"
    xmlns:d="http://schemas.microsoft.com/expression/blend/2008"
    xmlns:mc="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/markup-compatibility/2006"
    mc:Ignorable="d"
    Background="Transparent">

    <ScrollViewer>
        <RelativePanel Margin="0,0,0,0">
            <TextBlock x:Name="textblock1" Text="近期规划" FontWeight="Bold" 
                       FontSize="18"
                       Margin="0,0,0,10"/>
            <TextBlock x:Name="textblock2" Text="1.优化：登入系统、用户手册、工具箱"
                       TextWrapping="Wrap" Margin="0,0,0,5"
                       RelativePanel.Below="textblock1" RelativePanel.AlignLeftWithPanel="True" RelativePanel.AlignRightWithPanel="True"/>
            <TextBlock x:Name="textblock3" Text="2.适配夜间模式（页面字体颜色调整）"
                       TextWrapping="Wrap" Margin="0,0,0,5"               
                       RelativePanel.Below="textblock2" RelativePanel.AlignLeftWithPanel="True" RelativePanel.AlignRightWithPanel="True"/>
            <TextBlock x:Name="textblock4" Text="长期规划" FontWeight="Bold" RelativePanel.Below="textblock3"
                       FontSize="18"
                       Margin="0,20,0,10"/>
            <TextBlock x:Name="textblock5" Text="1.实现功能：词条编辑、讨论版重新渲染"
                       TextWrapping="Wrap" Margin="0,0,0,5"
                       RelativePanel.Below="textblock4" RelativePanel.AlignLeftWithPanel="True" RelativePanel.AlignRightWithPanel="True"/>
            <TextBlock x:Name="textblock6" Text="2.极大优化内存占用"
                       TextWrapping="Wrap" Margin="0,0,0,5"               
                       RelativePanel.Below="textblock5" RelativePanel.AlignLeftWithPanel="True" RelativePanel.AlignRightWithPanel="True"/>
            <TextBlock x:Name="textblock7" Text="碎碎念" FontWeight="Bold" RelativePanel.Below="textblock6"
                       FontSize="18"
                       Margin="0,20,0,10"/>
            <TextBlock x:Name="textblock8" Text="1.我看到原先的萌娘百科UWP应用在更换域名后无法使用，便着开始这个全新的UWP客户端开发（主要是联系不到作者，过去将近4年了吧）现在这个版本有很多不足，但我会在未来不断完善的。"
                       TextWrapping="Wrap" Margin="0,0,0,5"
                       RelativePanel.Below="textblock7" RelativePanel.AlignLeftWithPanel="True" RelativePanel.AlignRightWithPanel="True"/>
            <TextBlock x:Name="textblock9" Text="2.现在这个应用因为大量页面使用Webview，内存占用很不理想。那么早上架其实也是想抛砖引玉，看看大佬们有没有什么解决办法。后续开发完毕，会再尝试移植到桌面和安卓平台（似乎官方已经在重构移动应用）"
                       TextWrapping="Wrap" Margin="0,0,0,5"               
                       RelativePanel.Below="textblock8" RelativePanel.AlignLeftWithPanel="True" RelativePanel.AlignRightWithPanel="True"/>
        </RelativePanel>
    </ScrollViewer>
</Page>
